description:
There is a Hospital Emergency, they are running low on supplies and equipments.
It's up to you to save the day, or should I say, the night ! You love the night shift, usually the streets are desert and calm, but not on a full moon night.

You'll collect medic kit, monitors and oxygen tanks for all the patient at the hospital, since it's an emergency you'll have to make your siren work so the other vehicles know you're coming. If you don't warn them you'll end up crashing in them, it's really dangerous going high speed, but keep calm and time your buttons smashing correctly to be the best ambulance driver ! Have a Fun 911 Rush
